    126  0000 ????						; Original author: Manuel Rotschkar
    127  0000 ????						;
    128  0000 ????						; Sets a 2 byte RAM pointer to an absolute address.
    129  0000 ????						;
    130  0000 ????						; Usage: SET_POINTER pointer, address
    131  0000 ????						; Example: SET_POINTER SpritePTR, SpriteData
    132  0000 ????						;
